title: 500th Episode Call-In Spectacular!
description:
We did it—500 episodes! To celebrate, Sean, Amanda, and Bobby are taking your calls and answering your burning questions about their favorite episodes, movie theater experiences, Big-Pic bits, and the future of the show.

Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins
Producer: Bobby Wagner
